databaseTime - Static variable in interface Data_Access.Data
Used to handle default Timestamp storage in MySQL MySQL doesn't handle empty Time objects very well so it needs to be set to a default beforehand In this case an empty time like '0000-00-00' will be set to null in the database As of April 22nd this variable is only used in NoteDBConnect
